headline: Are Jack Henry & Associates' (JKHY) New Banno Integrations Quietly Redefining Its Competitive Moat?
summary: In late January 2026, Jack Henry announced new Banno Digital Platform enhancements, including native transaction enrichment via Bud Financial and embedded credit card management through CorServ, aimed at giving bank and credit union customers clearer transaction details and integrated card controls. These integrations highlight how Jack Henry is using its open Banno APIs and a broad fintech ecosystem to deepen data-driven, personalized digital banking experiences for approximately 7,400...
